      "body" : "Current Guava implementation is not worse than accepted answer: <a href=\"https://github.com/google/guava/blob/master/guava/src/com/google/common/collect/Streams.java#L60\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">github.com/google/guava/blob/master/guava/src/com/google/com&zwnj;&#8203;mon/&hellip;</a>"
